These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie
2 different games are played: domino, chess
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, october
House: tower, art-deco
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk       | mirinda    |
| Job           | journalist | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | thriller   |
| Game   | chess  | domino     |
| Birthday           | october       | september     |
| House     | tower     | art-deco        |

