.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
2 different games are played: poker, whist
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, may
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person drinking water is the person playing whist##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Game   | poker       | whist     |
| Cigar           | davidoff        | old-henry    |
| Birthday     | june  | may    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
