The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, boat
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, scientist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour
1. the engineer is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
